snippet.title: Buldhana Bus Accident | बुलढाणा बस अपघातातील मृतांवर आज सामूहिक अंत्यसंस्कार | Marathi News
snippet.description:
Mass funeral for Buldhana accident victims. Malegaon will be led by BJP MLA Nilesh Rane, Hindu Janakrosh Morcha will be held. Chief Minister Eknath Shinde, Deputy Chief Minister Devendra Fadnavis inaugurated various works under Mira Bhayander Mahapalika. Amit Thackeray will go to Gangapur in Sambhajinagar to inaugurate a school. Gurupurnima festival begins in Shirdi.

बुलढाणा अपघातातील मृतांवर होणार सामूहिक अंत्यसंस्कार. मालेगावला भाजप आमदार निलेश राणे यांच्या नेतृत्वाखाली हिंदू जनआक्रोश मोर्चा काढण्यात येणार आहे. मुख्यमंत्री एकनाथ शिंदे, उपमुख्यमंत्री देवेंद्र फडणवीस यांच्या हस्ते मीरा भाईंदर नगरपालिका अंतर्गत विविध कामांच्या भूमिपूजन लोकार्पण सोहळा. अमित ठाकरे हे संभाजीनगरमध्ये गंगापूरला एका शाळेच्या लोकार्पपणासाठी जाणार आहेत.शिर्डीत गुरुपौर्णिमा उत्सवाला सुरूवात.

snippet.title: क्या Bhide पकड़ पाएगा चोरों को? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Episode 2458 | 2 July 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Episode 2458: क्या Bhide पकड़ पाएगा चोरों को?
------------------------------------
Madhvi gives a head massage to Bhide using the oil given by Tappu. The oil works its magic and Bhide heads straight to the bed and falls asleep. Tappu returns to Gokuldham to accomplish the task of taking Sakaram out of society to learn to drive.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 2458
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #sonypal 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin 2nd Last Episode - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 143 | Raghav ने ली Pragati की जान! | Highlight
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 143 | Raghav ने ली Pragati की जान! | Highlight

Raghav takes his revenge on Pragati and kills him. Later, Pragati's father gets shocked to see snakes near the unconscious Pragati and gets confused. Soon Prasant arrives and reveals the truth to him. Will he be able to believe Prasant?

Naagin, the saga of love and revenge, sacrifice. This supernatural show traces the lives of 'ichchadhari' naagins. Watch on, as every season, the Naagin fights evil and keeps the ultimate source of power safe.

snippet.title: Types of Relatives | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Prepare to be entertained as we explore the typical assortment of relatives who grace Indian families with their presence. From the loving yet overprotective siblings to the mischievous and ever-curious aunts and uncles, this sketch video hilariously captures the essence of these distinctive personalities. If you have faced the same type of situations or you belong to a type of category, do let us know in the comments.

Rajesh Singpuriya "Bhole Baba Ki Machine 2 (Official Song)" Hansraj Railhan - New Haryanvi Song 2023

Song : Bhole Baba Ki Machine 2 (Official Song)
Singer : Rajesh Singpuria & Nitin Trikha
Writer : Rajesh Singpuria
Music : Gr Music
Composer : Rajesh Singpuria
Artist : Rajesh Singpuria, Hansraj Railhan, Divya Verma, Vanshika, Mohit, Sohit
Background Music : Rajesh Singpuria
DOP : Rajiv Singh, Deepak Bhardwaj& Abhi Chauhan 
Edit : Lucky Kajla
Makeup : Rajni Chaudhary
Choreographar : Parveen Nani
Spl Thanks : Night Life Paradise Mohan Chatti Risikesh 9467760790
Lable : Sonotek Music
Copyrights : Sonotek Cassettes Company

LIKE || COMMENT || SHARE || SUBSCRIBE


Make Your Instagram Reels On This Song - https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/(null)

#bholebabakimachine2
#Rajeshsingpuriabholesong
#sonotekmusic 
#rajeshsingpuriasong 
#haryanvisong

#kawadsong
#sawansong 

Song Lyrics :-

स्कीम स्कीम स्कीम
नीलकंठ त आयी स एक खबर बड़ी नमकीना भोलानाथ नोट छापण की सबनै दैव मशीन।
हाँ बच्चा नोट छापण की मशीन चाहिए,
 जी बाबा अच्छा अच्छा, 
बाबा बहोत दिन होगे मशीन मागते-भागते आज तो बाबा यो शुभ कार्य करै दो भगत को मशीन लाकै दो।
बाबा एक Request है, 
क्या Request है, 
बाबा हा - पाच दे दो, 
पाच मशीन, 
क्या करेगा पाच मशीनों का बाबा एक तो वो मेरी बेबे का छोरा है ना उस्तै दे प्यूगा अच्छा- अर एक मेरे मामा यी दे दयुगां, 
अर एक मेरा चाचा है. ना छोटे थाला वो भी गरीब सा ए आदमी है, 
एक उस्तै दे दयगे वो भी कमा रखा लेगा। हा हा अच्छा,
 एक मेरी माँ त्यी देदगे, 
एक मै / चला ट्यूगा,
 तेरी मौ चला लेगी, 
हा वा तो

साईकिल भी चला ले है। हा हा वाह रे भगत,
 वाह बेटा वाह,
 होगी ना पाच बाबा, 
मै कोए झूठ - बोलू मन्ने तो कोए ज्यादा लालच सा भी ना लेकिन बच्चा स्टोक मै त रही है।
 एक ही मशीन रह ना बाबा इब न्यू मतना करो फेर के बेरा आप कद आओगे, 
आज तो ले जाओ। क... न्यू मतना करो बाबा हवतो लगतै हाथा दे ये दो, 
एक मिलेगी, 
ना बाबा इब तो मै पाच ल्यूगा, 
पाच हा, एक मिलेगी, 
पाच ब्यूगा बाबा पाच ल्यूगा, 
बाबा, मशीन मागता होगा शर्म तो भाती नी होगी अरे पगली, 
आज मन्नै सुपने म बाबा दिखे है, 
अर सुबह का सपना कदै खाली नी जाया करे, 
चार साल होगे समझाती न क्यू मशीन के चक्कर मे पड़ा हुआ है और

क्यू और न मेर रखा है। बस थोड़ी सी
में गड़बड़ चालरी थी, आज शाम Calculation त्यी फैसला हो ज्यागा
बम भोले ओ..... बम मोले ओ.. बम-बम भोले बम बम भोले बम बम भोले
काम-धाम मै करता कोन्या साल हो लिए तीन मनै, 
काम करण का मूड ना बनता साल हो लिए तीन मन्नै भोलेनाथ नोट छापण कद-सी मिले मशीन मन्न।
भोलेनाथ नोट छापण की कद सी मिलै मशीन मनै । 
लगा-लगा क जोत बालदी या पूरा थी की दिन मनै, 
पक्की डेट बतादे भोते / कद सी मिले मशीन मनै- पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कदसी मिले मशीन मनै, 
बन भोते।
जिसकी किस्त नही भरनी हो इसा दवादे लोन मनै, 
ना करना पड़े रिचार्ज बाबा इसा


दवादे फोन मनै, मैं नोटा का प्यासा सू
बाबा धन का पाणी देदे नपी मशीन नही देता त मनै पुराणी देदे तू, कोए पुरापी दे दे तू। 
इमरू आले करणे होंगे सपने मेरे तू
रंगीन तनै, 
पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै। 
सौ के नोट न भी बाबा मै कभी-कभी दिना चलाउ सूं, मारे पड़ोसी काजू चाब और मै बुगडे खाऊ सू,
थारी आरती गाते. गाते थूक मेरा यो सूख लिया, 
धूप लावण के चक्कर मे कभी व कुडता फूक बिया-कची ब कुड़ता फूक लिया, 
इस सिंहपरिये की जरूर सुर्णेगा सौ परशेट यकीन मनै,
 पक्की डेट बतादे भोबे कद सी मिले मशीन मनै-पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै

भोले... र बच्चा चाहिए अगर मशीन वचन तनै भरणे होंगे तीन- वचन तन भरने धेरै तीन पहला वचन म छापने जितने छापे नोट, 
कभी मन मत ल्याइए खोट,
 मै ल्युगा डेली तेरी रिपोर्ट, करुगां हरकत सब तेरी नोट, 
अगर तनै घमंड दिखाया त, 
उनगर तनै चाप कमाया त, 
कोए बी गरीब सताया ता, 
किसे का दिल जो दुखाया व मै उस दिन तेरी बजादू बीन, 
खोसल्युगा म तेरी मशीन।
वचन- धर्म से दूर अगर हटगा, 
तेरा विश्वास अगर मिटगा, 
अगर श्रद्धा से तू कटगा फक्र मा-बाप को जा घटगा, 
श्योद दयूगा मै तेरी जमीन,
 खोसल्लूगा मै तेरी मशीन, 
अमर ये पर्णं पुगाओगे, 
अगर ये वचन निभाओगे कोई दुख पास ना भटकेगी, 
हमेशा खुशी मनाओगे। 
मै सवर्ण टैंक भी दे दयुगां, 
भगत का रैंक भी

दे दयुगां, 
मशीन की बात क्या करते हो तुम्हे
मै बैक भी दे ट्यूगा - तुम्हे मै बैक भी
दे दयुगो ।
बाबा यो के दिया नोट छापण की मशीन - मांगी थी, 
ये वही है इससे अच्छे-अच्छे गीत  लिखो और सोनोटेक मे जाके दो और नोट छापो, 
जैसा जिसका काम है उसको वैसी ही नोट छापण की मशीन मिलेगी।

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3812 | 1 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3812: Mall Ke Daam
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena is having a good time playing football during the monsoon season, but things get worse when they accidently hit Bhise with their ball. Bhide falls and is injured the second time the ball hits him so hard. Bhide is taken to Dr. Hathi by Madhavi and the kids, who verify that he has a slight injury. Tapu Sena feels sorry for Bhide and decides to stop playing. They proceed to apologize to Bhide but are surprised to discover him dancing in joy. Bhide lied about his ailment to Tapu Sena in order to keep them from playing football. Later, while purchasing vegetables from Sunita's booth, the Gokuldham Ladies notice a new scheme.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3812, 1 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Tapu Sena is having a good time playing football during the monsoon season, but things get worse when they accidently hit Bhise with their ball. Bhide falls and is injured the second time the ball hits him so hard. Bhide is taken to Dr. Hathi by Madhavi and the kids, who verify that he has a slight injury. Tapu Sena feels sorry for Bhide and decides to stop playing. They proceed to apologize to Bhide but are surprised to discover him dancing in joy. snippet.title: अजित पवार सरकार में शामिल! Ajit Pawar joins Maharashtra govt
snippet.description:
भाजपा से हाथ मिला लेने के बाद अजीत पवार ने कहा है कि उन्हें सब का आशीर्वाद हासिल है।उन्होंने नाम तो नहीं लिया कि शरद पवार का आशीर्वाद हासिल है या नहीं मगर कहा है कि आप इंतज़ार कीजिए और देखते जाइये। क्या अब यही देखना बाकी है कि शरद पवार भी चलते हुए बीजेपी में शामिल हो जाएंगे? यह मामला वैचारिक पतन का नहीं है। शिवसेना के साथ जा चुके हैं तो बीजेपी के साथ जा ही सकते हैं। लेकिन कहीं भी चले जाने वाले शरद पवार क्या विपक्ष की बैठक से लौट कर उस NCP के साथ चले जाएंगे जो अब बीजेपी की सरकार का हिस्सा है? अब यही देखना बाकी है। बिना अपनी पार्टी के शरद पवार विपक्षी एकता की राजनीति भी कैसे करेंगे। शरद पवार ने कहा है कि जनता के पास जाएंगे और फिर से नई पार्टी खड़ी करेंगे। क्या उनका बयान महाराष्ट्र में नई सियासी करवट लेने के लिए काफी है या फिर जो होना था वो हो चुका है। 2024 का चुनाव दिलचस्प होगा। उद्धव ठाकरे औऱ शरद पवार ज़ीरो से शुरूी करेंगे कया जनता उन्हें महाराष्ट्र का हीरो बनाएगी?

#maharashtra #ajitpawar #sharadpawar #devendrafadnavis #eknathshinde #amitshah #modi #ncp #ravishkumar

snippet.title: CM Shinde on Buldhana Bus Accident |अपघातग्रस्त विदर्भ ट्रॅव्हल्सच्या मालकांची प्रतिक्रिया
snippet.description:
A terrible accident of a passenger bus took place in Buldhana. 26 passengers have died on the spot. There were a total of 33 passengers in the bus. Eight of these passengers got out safely. The accident took place on Samrudhi Highway near Pimpalkhuta village near Sindkhedaraja in Buldhana district. This passenger bus was going from Nagpur to Pune. At that time, this terrible incident took place around half past midnight.

बुलढाण्यात (Buldhana) एका प्रवासी बसचा भीषण अपघात (Accident) झाल्याची घटना घडली. यामध्ये 26 प्रवाशांचा जागीच मृत्यू झाला आहे. बसमध्ये एकूण 33 प्रवासी होते. यातील आठ प्रवासी सुखरुप बाहेर पडले आहेत. बुलढाणा जिल्ह्यातील सिंदखेडराजाजवळ पिंपळखुटा गावालगत समृध्दी महामार्गावर हा अपघात झाला आहे. ही प्रवासी बस नागपूरहून पुण्याला निघाली होती. त्यावेळी रात्री दीड वाजण्याच्या सुमारास ही भीषण घटना घडली.

snippet.title: Keedaa Cola Official Teaser || Tharun Bhascker || #KeedaaColaTeaser
snippet.description:
Watch & Enjoy -- Keedaa Cola Official Teaser.

#KeedaaCola #KeedaaColaTeaser #TharunBhascker 

After #Pellichoopulu and #ENE, Tharun Bhascker is coming up with a wacky tale of crime, comedy of errors and unusual collaborations of weird, yet relatable characters. Keedaa Cola is an ultra-stylish crime comedy with a pinch of intense action and breathtaking moments. Dive into the world of #KeedaaCola with this teaser. 

Written & directed by Tharun Bhascker Dhaassyam
Produced by : K.Vivek Sudhanshu, Saikrishna Gadwal, Srinivas Kaushik Nanduri, Sripad Nandiraj & Upendra Varma.
Executive Producer : K.Vivek Sudhanshu, Saikrishna Gadwal & Srinivas Kaushik Nanduri.
Music : Vivek Sagar
Cinematography : AJ Aaron
Editor : Upendra Varma
Art Director: Ashish Teja Pulala
Sound Design : Varun Venugopal
Costumes : Poojitha Tadikonda 
Writers: Pranay Koppala, Ramya Kakumanu, Shanthan Raj & Tharun Bhascker
VFX : Nagu Talari & Ashok Mocharla.
PRO : Vamsi Shekar.
Marketing : Saikrishna Gadwal
Digital Agency : Ticket Factory & Hashtag Media

Suresh Productions (Telugu: సురేష్ ప్రొడక్షన్స్) is a film production company, a subsidiary of Rama Naidu Studios, founded by Dr. D. Ramanaidu. The production house of the company is Ramanaidu Studios which is located at Hyderabad. Suresh Productions, is one of India’s largest film production companies with over 50 years of contribution to national and regional cinema.

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Dune: Part Two | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Do what must be done. #DunePartTwo only in theaters November 3.

DUNE: PART TWO

The saga continues as award-winning filmmaker Denis Villeneuve embarks on “Dune: Part Two,” the next chapter of Frank Herbert’s celebrated novel Dune, with an expanded all-star international ensemble cast. The film, from Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures, is the highly anticipated follow-up to 2021’s six-time Academy Award-winning “Dune.”

The big-screen epic continues the adaptation of Frank Herbert’s acclaimed bestseller Dune with returning and new stars, including Oscar nominee Timothée Chalamet (“Wonka,” “Call Me by Your Name”), Zendaya (“Spider-Man: No Way Home,” “Malcolm & Marie,” “Euphoria”), Rebecca Ferguson (“Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning”), Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (“Avengers: End Game,” “Milk”), Oscar nominee Austin Butler (“Elvis,” “Once Upon A Time...In Hollywood”), Oscar nominee Florence Pugh (“Black Widow,” “Little Women”), Dave Bautista (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “Thor: Love and Thunder”), Oscar winner Christopher Walken (“The Deer Hunter,” “Hairspray”), Stephen McKinley Henderson (“Fences,” “Lady Bird”), Léa Seydoux (the “James Bond” franchise and “Crimes of the Future”), with Stellan Skarsgård (the “Mamma Mia!” films, “Avengers: Age of Ultron”), with Oscar nominee Charlotte Rampling (“45 Years,” “Assassin’s Creed”), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (“No Country for Old Men,” “Being the Ricardos”).

“Dune: Part Two” will explore the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a warpath of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, he endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.

Villeneuve directed from a screenplay he co-wrote with Jon Spaihts based on Herbert’s novel. The film is produced by Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Villeneuve, Tanya Lapointe and Patrick McCormick. The executive producers are Josh Grode, Herbert W. Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt, Kim Herbert, with Kevin J. Anderson serving as creative consultant.

Villeneuve is again collaborating with his “Dune” creatives: Oscar-winning director of photography Greig Fraser; Oscar-winning production designer Patrice Vermette; Oscar-winning editor Joe Walker; Oscar-winning visual effects supervisor Paul Lambert; Oscar-nominated costume designer Jacqueline West. Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer is again on hand to create the score.

“Dune: Part Two” was filmed on location in Budapest, Abu Dhabi, Jordan and Italy. The film is slated for a November 3, 2023 worldwide release from Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:

Jethalal is in tension thinking about Bawri’s habit of coming to Gada Electronics; he feels that it is because of her, Bagha is unable to concentrate on his work. However, Daya suggests Jethalal to tie the knots of Bawri and Bagha with each other and by doing this his problem will get solved! Want to know what happened next in the episode? Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Episode No: 1950
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi 

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #sab #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7Z_ML__3ZjsXAXE9KHMxTiZ

snippet.title: Tere Bin Last Episode Teaser - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Last Episode Teaser - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Uniform Civil Code Explained: इतनी हाय तौबा क्यों? | UCC | PM Modi | Indian Democracy | RJ Raunak
snippet.description:
Hours after Prime Minister Narendra Modi advocated for the nationwide implementation of the Uniform Civil Code (UCC), the All India Muslim Personal Law Board held an emergency online meeting late on Tuesday evening. During the meeting, the Islamic personal law body decided to oppose the proposed law, which seeks to formulate and implement a set of common personal laws for all the citizens of India regardless of their religion, caste, and creed.

During the online meeting attended by AIMPLB president Saifullah Rehmani; Maulana Khalid Rasheed Farangi Mahali, chairman of Islamic Centre of India and member of AIMPLB; AIMPLB lawyers; and among others -- the Muslim body agreed on presenting its views more powerfully in front of the Law Commission. At the meeting, the documents to be submitted to the Law Commision were also finalised.

In this video we'll talk about UCC and what difference it would bring into Indian Society. What was the history and how this code will be a historic decision?

Like the video and please Subscribe.

snippet.title: Daya ने Business में रखा अपना पहला कदम | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Randeep Hooda was invited to the show to give the winning prize to Sonu. Next day, Nattu Kaka calls Daya regarding a red dairy which was missing from the shop. Later, Daya comes to 'Gada Electronics' to give the diary and also helps Nattu Kaka in selling the electronic gadgets. Stay tuned for your daily dose of laughter.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 218
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Daya ने Business में रखा अपना पहला कदम | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
